orderTips: Use the 'New Legal Experience' format — pick a grilled protein + flavor style + two keto sides (broccoli, bok choy & kimchi)
Ask for 'simply prepared with lemon & olive oil' — zero carbs added and delicious
Cajun Blackened & Hot Butter and Garlic Herb Chimichurri are also keto-safe flavor styles
Skip rice pilaf, potato wedges, and fries — choose steamed broccoli or Thai bok choy & kimchi as sides
Greek Salad without chickpeas and Caesar without croutons are excellent bases — add any grilled protein
The raw bar is naturally very low carb — oysters, clams, shrimp cocktail, sashimi, and tuna tartare are all great
At brunch, order omelets without home fries — the Farmers Omelet and Cajun Shrimp Omelet are solid keto picks
